1
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:21,167
♪We'll face life's problems, always♪

2
00:00:23,872 --> 00:00:31,223
♪Beautiful moments help us
along the way♪

3
00:00:33,088 --> 00:00:36,490
♪I see your pain♪

4
00:00:37,267 --> 00:00:42,047
♪And your bravery too♪

5
00:00:49,376 --> 00:00:54,752
♪Some things we cannot just erase♪

6
00:00:57,632 --> 00:01:03,561
♪And there's no time
to get stuck on the past♪

7
00:01:06,859 --> 00:01:09,969
♪Greet the daylight♪

8
00:01:10,368 --> 00:01:12,960
♪Go to the free♪

9
00:01:13,076 --> 00:01:15,589
♪Let's cross the wind,
dance in the rain♪

10
00:01:15,685 --> 00:01:17,669
♪Let the stars illuminate♪

11
00:01:18,053 --> 00:01:20,165
♪In either way♪

12
00:01:22,021 --> 00:01:23,973
♪Tears and fears, happiness♪

13
00:01:24,069 --> 00:01:28,096
♪They are all part of the journey♪

14
00:01:30,547 --> 00:01:34,612
=Double Happiness=

15
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,991
=Episode 4=

16
00:01:39,431 --> 00:01:40,511
Easy, easy.

17
00:01:42,592 --> 00:01:43,672
I'm so mad.

18
00:01:44,672 --> 00:01:45,672
You gave birth

19
00:01:45,752 --> 00:01:46,312
to them both.

20
00:01:46,392 --> 00:01:48,312
How can Dami and Xiaomi be so different?

21
00:01:48,631 --> 00:01:49,752
I'll only buy Xiaomi things.

22
00:01:49,832 --> 00:01:51,192
Nothing for Qian Dami anymore.

23
00:01:51,991 --> 00:01:53,592
I want to return those things.

24
00:01:53,711 --> 00:01:54,511
Return them.

25
00:01:58,351 --> 00:01:59,351
Don't be mad.

26
00:02:00,071 --> 00:02:00,791
It's all my fault.

27
00:02:00,871 --> 00:02:02,271
I should've played blind.

28
00:02:02,672 --> 00:02:03,912
It ruined our good mood.

29
00:02:05,392 --> 00:02:06,312
Dad, Ms. Hu,

30
00:02:06,392 --> 00:02:07,592
my stomach hurts a bit.

31
00:02:07,672 --> 00:02:08,991
I want to go to the toilet.

32
00:02:09,071 --> 00:02:09,792
Then hurry up.

33
00:02:09,872 --> 00:02:10,591
You need Ms. Hu?

34
00:02:10,671 --> 00:02:11,991
No, I'm a big kid now.

35
00:02:12,071 --> 00:02:12,952
I'll be right back.

36
00:02:13,032 --> 00:02:13,591
We'll wait.

37
00:02:13,671 --> 00:02:14,352
Take it slow.

38
00:02:14,432 --> 00:02:15,071
Okay.

39
00:02:17,791 --> 00:02:18,592
Honey,

40
00:02:18,912 --> 00:02:19,591
I didn't expect

41
00:02:19,671 --> 00:02:21,312
Dami would actually defend me.

42
00:02:22,472 --> 00:02:24,071
She's young and easy to sweet-talk.

43
00:02:24,511 --> 00:02:25,312
Easy to sweet-talk?

44
00:02:25,671 --> 00:02:26,311
Look.

45
00:02:26,391 --> 00:02:27,471
It took so much money.

46
00:02:27,551 --> 00:02:28,912
Don't you realize the fact?

47
00:02:29,071 --> 00:02:29,951
No?

48
00:02:31,872 --> 00:02:32,871
It's small money.

49
00:02:32,951 --> 00:02:34,271
I'll compensate you later, okay?

50
00:02:34,351 --> 00:02:35,111
I will.

51
00:02:49,071 --> 00:02:49,912
Wait a moment.

52
00:02:53,472 --> 00:02:54,472
Speak up!

53
00:02:54,912 --> 00:02:55,712
Hello, Mom.

54
00:02:58,831 --> 00:02:59,512
Don't be mad

55
00:02:59,592 --> 00:03:00,872
at what I just said.

56
00:03:01,071 --> 00:03:02,192
Mom, don't worry.

57
00:03:02,272 --> 00:03:04,072
Dad treats me very well this time.

58
00:03:04,152 --> 00:03:05,752
He's bought me many things.

59
00:03:05,912 --> 00:03:06,551
And

60
00:03:06,631 --> 00:03:07,632
all those classes'

61
00:03:07,712 --> 00:03:08,232
fees?

62
00:03:08,312 --> 00:03:09,311
He's paid them all.

63
00:03:09,391 --> 00:03:11,032
He said I should register again.

64
00:03:11,391 --> 00:03:12,632
When I get home, I'll tell you

65
00:03:12,712 --> 00:03:13,472
the details.

66
00:03:16,432 --> 00:03:17,072
I need to go.

67
00:03:17,152 --> 00:03:17,951
See you.

68
00:03:19,152 --> 00:03:20,151
Take care of yourself.

69
00:03:20,231 --> 00:03:21,231
Don't play too long.

70
00:03:22,671 --> 00:03:23,551
Xu Kaixin.

71
00:03:24,831 --> 00:03:26,032
Did I hear that right?

72
00:03:27,752 --> 00:03:29,752
As expected of my daughter.

73
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:39,256
(My location to Happy Cake Shop)

74
00:03:53,032 --> 00:03:53,831
Sir.

75
00:03:55,272 --> 00:03:56,071
Sir.

76
00:03:56,791 --> 00:03:59,512
I want to buy a fruit basket.
Pick some good ones for me.

77
00:03:59,592 --> 00:04:00,432
Okay.

78
00:04:00,951 --> 00:04:01,591
For the bottom,

79
00:04:01,671 --> 00:04:02,912
get some apples

80
00:04:02,992 --> 00:04:04,671
or other cheaper fruits.

81
00:04:04,791 --> 00:04:05,632
For the top,

82
00:04:05,712 --> 00:04:07,831
get some slightly more expensive fruits.

83
00:04:08,111 --> 00:04:09,591
Make it both fancy and affordable.

84
00:04:09,671 --> 00:04:10,551
Okay.

85
00:04:10,631 --> 00:04:12,031
- Please wait here.
- Okay.

86
00:04:12,111 --> 00:04:13,072
It'll be ready soon.

87
00:04:13,152 --> 00:04:13,712
Okay.

88
00:04:13,872 --> 00:04:14,631
Bird's nest?

89
00:04:15,551 --> 00:04:16,632
Ejiao cubes?

90
00:04:17,512 --> 00:04:18,432
Dami is only eight.

91
00:04:18,512 --> 00:04:19,671
She can't possibly eat these.

92
00:04:20,551 --> 00:04:21,752
These are for me.

93
00:04:21,832 --> 00:04:22,632
Xu Kaixin,

94
00:04:23,032 --> 00:04:23,952
don't be so cheeky.

95
00:04:24,032 --> 00:04:24,952
I won't pay.

96
00:04:25,032 --> 00:04:26,272
Pay for it yourself.

97
00:04:26,832 --> 00:04:27,512
I'm just

98
00:04:27,592 --> 00:04:28,872
taking advantage of my daughter.

99
00:04:28,952 --> 00:04:29,911
Stop it.

100
00:04:29,991 --> 00:04:31,512
I'm buying things for Dami only.

101
00:04:31,592 --> 00:04:32,952
Let's eat hot pot today.

102
00:04:33,311 --> 00:04:34,351
Sure.

103
00:04:35,712 --> 00:04:37,111
I want to eat spicy hot pot.

104
00:04:38,632 --> 00:04:39,431
Excuse me.

105
00:04:41,592 --> 00:04:42,671
Weirdo.

106
00:04:45,551 --> 00:04:46,271
Why

107
00:04:46,351 --> 00:04:47,351
are hot guys' girlfriends

108
00:04:47,431 --> 00:04:48,312
all so ordinary?

109
00:04:48,392 --> 00:04:48,952
Yet nobody

110
00:04:49,032 --> 00:04:50,032
wants a beauty like me.

111
00:04:50,791 --> 00:04:52,192
She's not ordinary at all.

112
00:04:52,272 --> 00:04:54,072
She is very good-looking.

113
00:05:02,191 --> 00:05:03,351
Am I not good-looking?

114
00:05:03,551 --> 00:05:04,832
Paw Patrol, attention!

115
00:05:05,351 --> 00:05:06,671
Your task today

116
00:05:06,952 --> 00:05:08,952
is to find

117
00:05:09,512 --> 00:05:11,471
the captain's lost slipper

118
00:05:11,551 --> 00:05:12,431
and bring it back.

119
00:05:13,991 --> 00:05:15,272
If you find it,

120
00:05:15,472 --> 00:05:16,271
you'll be rewarded.

121
00:05:16,351 --> 00:05:16,952
Okay?

122
00:05:17,032 --> 00:05:17,552
Okay.

123
00:05:17,632 --> 00:05:19,832
Now, heed Captain Ryder's order.

124
00:05:20,431 --> 00:05:22,512
Paw Patrol, move out!

125
00:05:33,632 --> 00:05:34,472
I'm taking a break.

126
00:05:38,311 --> 00:05:39,431
Did you find it?

127
00:05:39,871 --> 00:05:40,671
No.

128
00:05:41,871 --> 00:05:42,712
Hurry up.

129
00:05:43,392 --> 00:05:44,231
You need to find it.

130
00:05:47,592 --> 00:05:48,472
Where is it?

131
00:05:51,751 --> 00:05:53,392
Take it out quickly.

132
00:05:53,472 --> 00:05:55,032
I can't believe you.

133
00:05:55,152 --> 00:05:56,471
It's for me to catch a breath

134
00:05:56,551 --> 00:05:57,912
and take a rest, okay?

135
00:05:58,191 --> 00:05:59,192
You know what?

136
00:05:59,272 --> 00:06:00,911
For these two little ones,

137
00:06:00,991 --> 00:06:01,832
my heart problem

138
00:06:01,912 --> 00:06:03,231
almost flared up.

139
00:06:04,632 --> 00:06:05,512
Whose fault is that?

140
00:06:06,191 --> 00:06:07,952
You rushed to the next building

141
00:06:08,152 --> 00:06:09,072
early in the morning

142
00:06:09,152 --> 00:06:10,431
to get the kids over here.

143
00:06:11,032 --> 00:06:12,431
Without the skills,

144
00:06:12,512 --> 00:06:14,311
you tried to handle a difficult task.

145
00:06:20,152 --> 00:06:21,032
Think about it.

146
00:06:22,032 --> 00:06:23,271
In this family,

147
00:06:23,351 --> 00:06:25,471
three grown-ups make no other movement

148
00:06:25,551 --> 00:06:26,271
besides breathing

149
00:06:26,351 --> 00:06:27,871
day after day.

150
00:06:28,431 --> 00:06:29,671
Looking at Yu'an and Yule

151
00:06:29,751 --> 00:06:31,032
reminds me

152
00:06:31,751 --> 00:06:33,271
of Youyou and her sister

153
00:06:33,351 --> 00:06:34,431
in the past.

154
00:06:36,632 --> 00:06:37,472
It was so wonderful.

155
00:06:41,392 --> 00:06:42,191
Moreover,

156
00:06:43,032 --> 00:06:45,032
Mei Chengyi wants to remarry.

157
00:06:45,751 --> 00:06:46,911
We don't know

158
00:06:46,991 --> 00:06:48,231
about the woman at all.

159
00:06:48,952 --> 00:06:50,432
Will she be like us,

160
00:06:50,512 --> 00:06:52,152
tolerant of the kids all the time?

161
00:06:52,392 --> 00:06:54,632
What if she makes them suffer secretly?

162
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:56,912
Shouldn't I spoil the kids a bit more?

163
00:06:57,311 --> 00:06:58,671
Come on.

164
00:06:59,472 --> 00:07:01,152
Your two perfect angels

165
00:07:01,392 --> 00:07:02,952
who look sweet to outsiders are in fact

166
00:07:03,032 --> 00:07:04,031
little schemers.

167
00:07:04,111 --> 00:07:05,632
They won't be at a disadvantage.

168
00:07:05,832 --> 00:07:07,231
That's not necessarily true.

169
00:07:11,311 --> 00:07:12,231
Oh no.

170
00:07:12,392 --> 00:07:13,632
They've made trouble again.

171
00:07:18,191 --> 00:07:19,432
It's lowercase c.

172
00:07:19,512 --> 00:07:21,031
Great-aunt, you said it wrong.

173
00:07:21,111 --> 00:07:21,952
I'm upset.

174
00:07:22,392 --> 00:07:23,231
Why are you upset?

175
00:07:23,311 --> 00:07:25,231
Look, you read it wrong.

176
00:07:26,272 --> 00:07:27,032
Hello, are you...

177
00:07:28,991 --> 00:07:30,512
Qin Sulan, what are you here for?

178
00:07:30,791 --> 00:07:32,752
I'm here to see my grandson, Xiaomi.

179
00:07:32,832 --> 00:07:33,752
Are you snatching him?

180
00:07:33,832 --> 00:07:34,832
I'm telling you.

181
00:07:34,912 --> 00:07:36,911
We have surveillance here.
So don't do that.

182
00:07:36,991 --> 00:07:37,752
Don't joke.

183
00:07:37,832 --> 00:07:39,111
Why would I snatch him?

184
00:07:39,191 --> 00:07:39,832
As you know,

185
00:07:39,912 --> 00:07:41,192
we are all cultured people.

186
00:07:41,272 --> 00:07:43,032
I wouldn't do such a thing.

187
00:07:43,512 --> 00:07:44,952
I'm here to see Xiaomi.

188
00:07:45,032 --> 00:07:45,872
I've missed you.

189
00:07:45,952 --> 00:07:47,351
Here, look.

190
00:07:47,431 --> 00:07:48,152
These are for you.

191
00:07:48,871 --> 00:07:49,471
Xiaomi,

192
00:07:49,551 --> 00:07:51,512
look at the airplane I bought for you.

193
00:07:51,592 --> 00:07:53,512
It's your favorite airplane.

194
00:07:54,712 --> 00:07:55,632
What's wrong with you?

195
00:07:55,712 --> 00:07:57,472
Why don't you recognize me?

196
00:07:57,751 --> 00:07:59,551
You don't love me at all.

197
00:08:00,032 --> 00:08:01,271
You're talking nonsense.

198
00:08:01,351 --> 00:08:03,312
I love you the most.

199
00:08:03,392 --> 00:08:05,632
You are my treasure.

200
00:08:05,832 --> 00:08:07,311
I know everything.

201
00:08:08,111 --> 00:08:10,272
Dad never pays child support.

202
00:08:10,472 --> 00:08:12,632
It's Mom who raises my sister and me.

203
00:08:12,712 --> 00:08:14,431
You don't really love me.

204
00:08:14,832 --> 00:08:16,832
That's not true.

205
00:08:17,712 --> 00:08:18,711
Your dad and I

206
00:08:18,791 --> 00:08:20,952
are planning to save a lot,

207
00:08:21,032 --> 00:08:21,911
all for Xiaomi.

208
00:08:21,991 --> 00:08:22,552
How about it?

209
00:08:26,032 --> 00:08:26,832
Sweeties,

210
00:08:26,912 --> 00:08:28,152
let's go into the room.

211
00:08:28,472 --> 00:08:30,031
Grandpa still needs to clean up.

212
00:08:30,111 --> 00:08:31,031
Don't get hurt.

213
00:08:31,111 --> 00:08:32,312
Good girls.

214
00:08:32,392 --> 00:08:33,791
Come on in.

215
00:08:40,512 --> 00:08:41,112
Youyou.

216
00:08:42,032 --> 00:08:42,752
Get up.

217
00:08:43,352 --> 00:08:43,992
Youyou?

218
00:08:45,392 --> 00:08:46,152
Youyou?

219
00:08:46,272 --> 00:08:47,551
Time to get up.

220
00:08:47,632 --> 00:08:48,152
This home

221
00:08:48,232 --> 00:08:49,391
is all in a mess.

222
00:08:49,471 --> 00:08:51,152
You don't even come out and help.

223
00:08:52,191 --> 00:08:54,152
Stop this night-for-day nonsense.

224
00:08:54,992 --> 00:08:55,791
Get up.

225
00:08:56,711 --> 00:08:59,112
- What?
- What are you doing?

226
00:08:59,632 --> 00:09:01,711
Don't take it out on the kid
when you're tired.

227
00:09:01,831 --> 00:09:03,511
Do you have a grudge against each other?

228
00:09:03,591 --> 00:09:04,432
It's the weekend.

229
00:09:04,512 --> 00:09:05,992
What's wrong with sleeping in?

230
00:09:06,431 --> 00:09:07,791
Focus on your things.

231
00:09:07,912 --> 00:09:09,351
You're spoiling her.

232
00:09:09,431 --> 00:09:10,591
"What's wrong"?

233
00:09:11,392 --> 00:09:12,791
Don't you know she is ill?

234
00:09:13,112 --> 00:09:14,912
She is mentally ill.

235
00:09:16,311 --> 00:09:17,711
Which young woman in her twenties

236
00:09:17,791 --> 00:09:19,392
doesn't work?

237
00:09:19,632 --> 00:09:20,231
Every day,

238
00:09:20,311 --> 00:09:21,912
she plays games day and night.

239
00:09:21,992 --> 00:09:23,551
My daughter works.

240
00:09:23,632 --> 00:09:25,351
She is the senior housekeeper here.

241
00:09:25,431 --> 00:09:27,032
This is a new term abroad.

242
00:09:27,112 --> 00:09:28,112
Understand?

243
00:09:28,431 --> 00:09:29,232
Nonsense.

244
00:09:29,591 --> 00:09:31,112
We're just ordinary people.

245
00:09:31,311 --> 00:09:32,351
We need no housekeeper.

246
00:09:32,431 --> 00:09:33,752
Let alone a senior one.

247
00:09:34,311 --> 00:09:35,272
Besides,

248
00:09:35,352 --> 00:09:36,591
even if we're hiring,

249
00:09:36,671 --> 00:09:37,832
she has to apply.

250
00:09:37,912 --> 00:09:38,552
Hiring her

251
00:09:38,632 --> 00:09:40,752
is no better
than hiring a live-in nanny.

252
00:09:41,071 --> 00:09:42,391
With 6,000 or 7,000 yuan a month,

253
00:09:42,471 --> 00:09:43,032
a nanny

254
00:09:43,112 --> 00:09:44,351
can do everything well for us.

255
00:09:44,431 --> 00:09:45,672
She only puts on airs with me.

256
00:09:45,752 --> 00:09:46,832
And she asks for more money

257
00:09:46,912 --> 00:09:48,032
if I ask her for a favor.

258
00:09:48,311 --> 00:09:49,511
And you just casually

259
00:09:49,591 --> 00:09:51,191
find reasons to give her money.

260
00:09:54,112 --> 00:09:55,632
I'm glad to give my daughter money.

261
00:09:56,032 --> 00:09:56,792
Kick us out

262
00:09:56,872 --> 00:09:57,992
if you have the guts.

263
00:09:58,431 --> 00:09:59,791
You can keep your money well.

264
00:10:03,112 --> 00:10:04,752
I'm reasoning with you.

265
00:10:05,671 --> 00:10:07,112
You are playing rogue with me.

266
00:10:10,831 --> 00:10:11,791
Just spoil her.

267
00:10:12,711 --> 00:10:14,431
One day you'll regret it.

268
00:10:34,352 --> 00:10:35,192
Are you satisfied?

269
00:10:35,272 --> 00:10:36,392
We've bought so many things.

270
00:10:36,632 --> 00:10:37,431
I'm happy.

271
00:10:37,831 --> 00:10:38,591
Happy, huh?

272
00:10:40,471 --> 00:10:41,752
Hello, Uncle.

273
00:10:44,752 --> 00:10:45,272
Okay.

274
00:10:45,791 --> 00:10:46,296
Okay.

275
00:10:46,632 --> 00:10:47,191
What's up?

276
00:10:47,632 --> 00:10:48,312
My uncle wants us

277
00:10:48,392 --> 00:10:49,312
to eat at his place.

278
00:10:49,392 --> 00:10:50,872
Tell him we'll be there soon.

279
00:10:51,632 --> 00:10:52,631
Do you want to anger him?

280
00:10:52,711 --> 00:10:53,551
She's with us.

281
00:10:58,912 --> 00:10:59,711
Well.

282
00:10:59,912 --> 00:11:01,032
I have something to do now.

283
00:11:01,112 --> 00:11:02,391
I'll send you back to your mom's

284
00:11:02,471 --> 00:11:03,032
place for now.

285
00:11:03,152 --> 00:11:04,591
When I'm done with my things,

286
00:11:04,711 --> 00:11:05,392
I promise

287
00:11:05,632 --> 00:11:07,032
you can come back anytime.

288
00:11:08,232 --> 00:11:08,872
Okay.

289
00:11:12,272 --> 00:11:12,831
Alright.

290
00:11:18,872 --> 00:11:19,711
Here is 500 yuan.

291
00:11:20,112 --> 00:11:22,512
Your pocket money.

292
00:11:23,791 --> 00:11:24,832
Take it, okay?

293
00:11:24,912 --> 00:11:25,632
Keep it well.

294
00:11:27,392 --> 00:11:28,152
Okay.

295
