00:22:32,912 --> 00:22:34,312
people wouldn't even employ me.

589
00:22:36,312 --> 00:22:38,112
In that case, I won't comfort you.

590
00:22:39,031 --> 00:22:40,631
You do need to go out

591
00:22:40,711 --> 00:22:41,991
and see the sunlight.

592
00:22:42,112 --> 00:22:43,391
You can't totally disconnect

593
00:22:43,471 --> 00:22:45,032
from society and isolate yourself.

594
00:22:45,112 --> 00:22:46,592
You came back from abroad.

595
00:22:47,072 --> 00:22:47,951
You've seen the world.

596
00:22:48,031 --> 00:22:49,112
And you're well-educated.

597
00:22:49,392 --> 00:22:51,431
It's not hard for you
to reintegrate into society.

598
00:22:53,671 --> 00:22:54,751
Chengyi, do you know

599
00:22:55,872 --> 00:22:57,431
why I ended up like this?

600
00:23:04,751 --> 00:23:05,592
It's your sister.

601
00:23:07,951 --> 00:23:08,951
How do you know?

602
00:23:10,191 --> 00:23:11,592
I went through the same thing.

603
00:23:15,592 --> 00:23:16,232
I met her

604
00:23:16,312 --> 00:23:17,591
when we were 19

605
00:23:17,671 --> 00:23:18,471
in college.

606
00:23:20,031 --> 00:23:22,152
16 years have passed in a blink.

607
00:23:24,072 --> 00:23:25,751
Your sister was like a ray of light.

608
00:23:27,072 --> 00:23:27,991
She was so gentle

609
00:23:29,231 --> 00:23:30,231
and so powerful.

610
00:23:33,031 --> 00:23:33,951
As you know,

611
00:23:34,471 --> 00:23:35,832
we were deeply in love.

612
00:23:37,231 --> 00:23:38,031
Then suddenly...

613
00:23:41,112 --> 00:23:42,511
I found it hard to move on as well.

614
00:23:44,711 --> 00:23:46,312
But I still have Yu'an and Yule.

615
00:23:46,552 --> 00:23:48,191
No matter what, I must stand up.

616
00:23:52,751 --> 00:23:53,751
You're right.

617
00:23:55,552 --> 00:23:59,552
My sister had always been like
a ray of light.

618
00:24:00,312 --> 00:24:01,912
She seemed to be always

619
00:24:02,191 --> 00:24:03,511
living diligently

620
00:24:03,951 --> 00:24:05,112
and loving diligently.

621
00:24:06,991 --> 00:24:07,712
My parents

622
00:24:07,792 --> 00:24:09,392
always preferred my sister.

623
00:24:09,592 --> 00:24:10,991
But I never got jealous.

624
00:24:12,031 --> 00:24:13,112
Because I know

625
00:24:14,031 --> 00:24:15,312
my sister loved me a lot too.

626
00:24:19,832 --> 00:24:21,352
I just don't understand

627
00:24:21,991 --> 00:24:23,631
why someone who lived so diligently

628
00:24:23,711 --> 00:24:25,351
would end up like this.

629
00:24:25,431 --> 00:24:26,032
Then what's

630
00:24:26,112 --> 00:24:27,312
the point of me trying?

631
00:24:28,552 --> 00:24:30,112
People are going to die anyways.

632
00:24:30,431 --> 00:24:31,312
I might as well

633
00:24:31,711 --> 00:24:33,552
just do what I want

634
00:24:33,951 --> 00:24:35,031
and not settle.

635
00:24:40,792 --> 00:24:42,152
Think about it from another angle.

636
00:24:43,792 --> 00:24:45,191
Since you're going to die anyways,

637
00:24:45,431 --> 00:24:46,431
why not do

638
00:24:46,511 --> 00:24:47,751
what you want to do?

639
00:24:48,711 --> 00:24:49,472
I just don't know

640
00:24:49,552 --> 00:24:50,912
what I like

641
00:24:51,312 --> 00:24:52,431
or what I want to do.

642
00:24:53,031 --> 00:24:54,632
Then go find out.

643
00:24:55,711 --> 00:24:57,392
At least you have to go out first.

644
00:24:58,152 --> 00:24:59,032
Your sister and you

645
00:24:59,112 --> 00:24:59,752
are different.

646
00:24:59,832 --> 00:25:00,712
If you do miss her,

647
00:25:00,792 --> 00:25:02,031
go out and walk around.

648
00:25:02,471 --> 00:25:03,312
Go see the places

649
00:25:03,392 --> 00:25:04,591
she once liked for her.

650
00:25:04,671 --> 00:25:05,792
Won't that be great?

651
00:25:15,632 --> 00:25:16,312
See?

652
00:25:16,392 --> 00:25:17,951
My uncle is good to us, right?

653
00:25:18,112 --> 00:25:19,871
He's tough on the outside
and soft inside.

654
00:25:19,951 --> 00:25:21,312
He keeps nagging.

655
00:25:21,392 --> 00:25:22,472
But we got the certificate

656
00:25:22,552 --> 00:25:23,912
pretty soon.

657
00:25:24,072 --> 00:25:25,632
We must properly thank my uncle.

658
00:25:30,951 --> 00:25:31,711
Are you happy?

659
00:25:37,592 --> 00:25:39,392
You park the car.
I'll wait for you here.

660
00:25:47,152 --> 00:25:48,231
What are you doing?

661
00:25:48,991 --> 00:25:50,031
I'm going to my mom's.

662
00:25:51,152 --> 00:25:52,032
Then I'll go with you.

663
00:25:52,112 --> 00:25:52,951
No.

664
00:25:53,031 --> 00:25:54,111
My mom speaks harshly.

665
00:25:54,191 --> 00:25:54,951
If she upsets you,

666
00:25:55,031 --> 00:25:56,431
it will upset your uncle.

667
00:25:59,152 --> 00:25:59,951
Qian Hao!

668
00:26:00,152 --> 00:26:01,792
Are you kicking me away like a ladder?

669
00:26:04,552 --> 00:26:06,031
I won't stoop to your level.

670
00:26:06,912 --> 00:26:07,711
Chengyi,

671
00:26:08,431 --> 00:26:09,871
did they ask you to bring your date

672
00:26:09,951 --> 00:26:11,392
here for dinner this weekend?

673
00:26:13,031 --> 00:26:14,312
They said another weekend.

674
00:26:15,152 --> 00:26:15,911
Don't worry.

675
00:26:15,991 --> 00:26:17,031
I've got everything ready.

676
00:26:17,352 --> 00:26:18,032
I found a friend

677
00:26:18,112 --> 00:26:19,711
who studies acting to act for me.

678
00:26:20,552 --> 00:26:21,312
It's free.

679
00:26:22,392 --> 00:26:23,632
It's not that simple.

680
00:26:23,951 --> 00:26:25,072
When you went out on a date,

681
00:26:25,152 --> 00:26:26,711
my dad's colleague took a photo of you.

682
00:26:27,072 --> 00:26:28,232
To not be exposed,

683
00:26:28,312 --> 00:26:29,232
you'll have to get

684
00:26:29,312 --> 00:26:30,751
that woman from that day.

685
00:26:31,352 --> 00:26:32,152
What?

686
00:26:32,872 --> 00:26:33,711
That woman?

687
00:26:34,431 --> 00:26:35,552
She has to act.

688
00:26:47,271 --> 00:26:48,552
Mom, Lili,

689
00:26:48,632 --> 00:26:49,352
