690
00:26:49,511 --> 00:26:50,351
Xiaomi is asleep.

691
00:26:50,431 --> 00:26:51,631
Dami, why are you at home?

692
00:26:51,711 --> 00:26:52,472
Didn't you say

693
00:26:52,552 --> 00:26:54,392
you'd stay at your dad's for a few days?

694
00:26:55,912 --> 00:26:57,232
Dad said he has something to do

695
00:26:57,312 --> 00:26:57,951
and told me

696
00:26:58,031 --> 00:26:59,392
to come back before going back.

697
00:27:01,231 --> 00:27:02,351
Mom, I didn't lie to you.

698
00:27:02,431 --> 00:27:03,111
There's money.

699
00:27:03,191 --> 00:27:04,152
I've checked.

700
00:27:04,431 --> 00:27:05,712
I've brought back the gifts too.

701
00:27:05,792 --> 00:27:06,512
There's a lot.

702
00:27:06,592 --> 00:27:08,112
Alright, let's talk outside.

703
00:27:12,792 --> 00:27:13,431
Dad,

704
00:27:13,511 --> 00:27:14,032
do you

705
00:27:14,112 --> 00:27:15,592
need our help with anything?

706
00:27:16,072 --> 00:27:17,152
You two, come here.

707
00:27:17,431 --> 00:27:18,272
Take cleaning cloths

708
00:27:18,352 --> 00:27:19,751
and go clean the table.

709
00:27:23,392 --> 00:27:24,072
Come on.

710
00:27:24,152 --> 00:27:25,552
I will pick them up for you.

711
00:27:25,751 --> 00:27:26,328
Okay.

712
00:27:26,991 --> 00:27:28,991
Look at these two little ingrates.

713
00:27:30,152 --> 00:27:32,471
You bully me when you're with me.

714
00:27:33,031 --> 00:27:34,072
But in front of your dad,

715
00:27:34,152 --> 00:27:35,752
you're as obedient

716
00:27:35,832 --> 00:27:37,752
as two little rabbits.

717
00:27:37,832 --> 00:27:40,352
You do housework
and don't wreck the place anymore.

718
00:27:42,592 --> 00:27:43,992
It really breaks my heart

719
00:27:44,072 --> 00:27:45,671
to pieces.

720
00:27:48,152 --> 00:27:49,632
Chengyi, don't worry.

721
00:27:50,271 --> 00:27:51,072
Listen.

722
00:27:51,392 --> 00:27:52,472
Just find an excuse.

723
00:27:52,552 --> 00:27:54,792
You can say she's on a business trip

724
00:27:55,112 --> 00:27:55,991
or she's sick.

725
00:27:56,231 --> 00:27:57,512
Just push this thing aside

726
00:27:57,592 --> 00:27:58,632
for now.

727
00:28:00,031 --> 00:28:00,991
It's useless.

728
00:28:03,431 --> 00:28:04,872
He's your dad.

729
00:28:05,031 --> 00:28:06,352
Don't you know him?

730
00:28:07,231 --> 00:28:08,191
You can run,

731
00:28:08,271 --> 00:28:09,431
but you can't hide.

732
00:28:09,912 --> 00:28:11,552
He'll know about this sooner or later.

733
00:28:11,671 --> 00:28:12,832
If he becomes suspicious,

734
00:28:13,152 --> 00:28:15,152
he'll drag us both along.

735
00:28:15,392 --> 00:28:16,832
Then there's only one solution.

736
00:28:17,792 --> 00:28:18,792
Figure out a way

737
00:28:18,872 --> 00:28:20,471
to add that woman back on WeChat.

738
00:28:20,751 --> 00:28:22,792
And politely ask her.

739
00:28:23,511 --> 00:28:24,151
Alright.

740
00:28:24,231 --> 00:28:25,872
That's it.

741
00:28:26,711 --> 00:28:27,511
Eat some fruit.

742
00:28:28,112 --> 00:28:29,472
Alright, come quickly.

743
00:28:29,552 --> 00:28:30,632
Sweeties, hurry.

744
00:28:31,072 --> 00:28:31,792
Come quickly.

745
00:28:31,872 --> 00:28:32,792
Eat some fruit.

746
00:28:36,711 --> 00:28:38,272
Lili, are you comfortable?

747
00:28:38,352 --> 00:28:39,832
I bought this especially for you.

748
00:28:40,431 --> 00:28:41,032
Didn't you say

749
00:28:41,112 --> 00:28:42,351
you were living with your dad?

750
00:28:42,431 --> 00:28:44,431
Mom, you're silly, but I'm not.

751
00:28:44,872 --> 00:28:46,431
Business is business.

752
00:28:46,711 --> 00:28:47,472
But in the mall,

753
00:28:47,552 --> 00:28:48,671
you said differently.

754
00:28:48,751 --> 00:28:49,552
Ms. Hu Xiaojiao

755
00:28:49,632 --> 00:28:50,591
is my dad's new wife.

756
00:28:50,671 --> 00:28:52,112
You can't bully her.

757
00:28:52,511 --> 00:28:54,112
The main thing is to live.

758
00:28:54,552 --> 00:28:56,471
Money is certainly important,

759
00:28:56,711 --> 00:28:57,912
but being a person...

760
00:28:58,191 --> 00:28:59,032
Let me ask you again.

761
00:28:59,112 --> 00:29:00,991
We need to live, right?

762
00:29:01,751 --> 00:29:02,512
Well said.

763
00:29:02,592 --> 00:29:03,152
That's it.

764
00:29:05,152 --> 00:29:05,991
Come back.

765
00:29:06,991 --> 00:29:08,191
Did you tell your brother

766
00:29:08,392 --> 00:29:09,512
about all your wicked ideas?

767
00:29:09,592 --> 00:29:10,272
Sure.

768
00:29:10,352 --> 00:29:11,871
I have to worry about my whole family.

769
00:29:11,951 --> 00:29:13,472
Xiaomi is much smarter than you all.

770
00:29:13,552 --> 00:29:15,431
He learned and understood right away.

771
00:29:15,511 --> 00:29:16,792
Now she is cocky.

772
00:29:18,872 --> 00:29:20,112
Is this real or not?

773
00:29:23,112 --> 00:29:24,231
Every day,

774
00:29:24,951 --> 00:29:26,511
I take more pills than food.

775
00:29:30,951 --> 00:29:31,751
Mom,

776
00:29:33,671 --> 00:29:34,272
I think

777
00:29:34,352 --> 00:29:35,471
something is a bit off.

778
00:29:36,832 --> 00:29:37,632
What's wrong?

779
00:29:39,511 --> 00:29:40,312
Hu Xiaojiao

780
00:29:40,392 --> 00:29:41,632
said something that is correct.

781
00:29:42,031 --> 00:29:43,671
We haven't gotten much,

782
00:29:43,751 --> 00:29:45,391
but tens of thousands are already spent.

783
00:29:45,471 --> 00:29:46,792
If it goes on like this,

784
00:29:46,872 --> 00:29:47,631
our family fortune

785
00:29:47,711 --> 00:29:48,431
will all be taken

786
00:29:48,511 --> 00:29:49,671
by Dami and Xiaomi.

787
00:29:50,191 --> 00:29:52,471
Hu Xiaojiao is up to no good.

788
00:29:53,152 --> 00:29:54,191
She can't have children.

789
00:29:54,271 --> 00:29:55,991
She's jealous of your father-kids bond.

790
00:29:57,671 --> 00:29:58,911
As for Xu Kaixin,

791
00:29:58,991 --> 00:30:00,312
you know her well.

792
00:30:00,392 --> 00:30:02,231
She's carefree and foolish.

793
00:30:02,392 --> 00:30:03,792
That's why she was made a fool of

794
00:30:03,872 --> 00:30:05,592
by you during the divorce.

795
00:30:05,832 --> 00:30:06,632
I...

796
00:30:08,872 --> 00:30:10,511
I'm not worried about Xu Kaixin now.

797
00:30:10,751 --> 00:30:11,872
But don't forget

798
00:30:12,191 --> 00:30:13,031
Dami and Xiaomi

799
00:30:13,312 --> 00:30:15,191
carry the blood of our family.

800
00:30:15,392 --> 00:30:16,191
They are sharp.

801
00:30:16,312 --> 00:30:17,792
I'm starting to realize now.

802
00:30:17,872 --> 00:30:19,271
I don't think they are simple.

803
00:30:19,792 --> 00:30:21,191
Isn't that right?

804
00:30:21,352 --> 00:30:21,992
That shows

805
00:30:22,072 --> 00:30:23,312
Xiaomi is clever.

806
00:30:23,392 --> 00:30:24,191
Right?

807
00:30:24,991 --> 00:30:26,431
Spending some money for my grandson

808
00:30:26,511 --> 00:30:27,951
is completely right.

809
00:30:28,031 --> 00:30:29,471
What's wrong with that, right?

810
00:30:31,031 --> 00:30:32,832
Given my illness,

811
00:30:32,912 --> 00:30:34,111
my days are counted.

812
00:30:34,191 --> 00:30:36,191
Money is just external possessions,

813
00:30:36,431 --> 00:30:36,991
isn't it?

814
00:30:37,392 --> 00:30:38,312
I'm thinking,

815
00:30:38,392 --> 00:30:39,512
how can the money

816
00:30:39,592 --> 00:30:41,431
be spent on Xiaomi?

817
00:30:41,592 --> 00:30:42,712
That's debatable.

818
00:30:42,792 --> 00:30:43,951
Spending some money is okay,

819
00:30:44,031 --> 00:30:45,552
but we need to change our approach.

820
00:30:45,632 --> 00:30:47,392
Never ante up without seeing the flop.

821
00:30:47,552 --> 00:30:48,111
From now on,

822
00:30:48,191 --> 00:30:49,992
before we get the custody

823
00:30:50,072 --> 00:30:51,271
of the kids,

824
00:30:51,392 --> 00:30:53,832
we should always be careful
when spending more than 1,000.

825
00:30:56,031 --> 00:30:56,832
How about

826
00:30:57,312 --> 00:30:59,392
I go to talk to Xu Kaixin

827
00:30:59,552 --> 00:31:01,111
to see exactly how much money is needed

828
00:31:01,191 --> 00:31:02,631
for her to give Xiaomi to us.

829
00:31:02,711 --> 00:31:03,511
It's useless.

830
00:31:03,912 --> 00:31:05,392
I know Xu Kaixin the best.

831
00:31:05,832 --> 00:31:07,912
If money can really solve the problem,

832
00:31:08,031 --> 00:31:09,832
I can give her half of that condo.

833
00:31:10,271 --> 00:31:11,392
But once that woman

834
00:31:11,832 --> 00:31:13,231
becomes stubborn,

835
00:31:14,112 --> 00:31:14,912
she'll be tricky.

836
00:31:16,191 --> 00:31:17,592
I have to think of other ways.

837
00:31:18,552 --> 00:31:19,872
I have to make her feel that

838
00:31:20,152 --> 00:31:21,072
raising two kids alone

839
00:31:21,152 --> 00:31:22,191
is too much pressure

840
00:31:23,671 --> 00:31:24,871
to make her give the custody

841
00:31:24,951 --> 00:31:26,512
to us for Xiaomi's future willingly.

842
00:31:26,592 --> 00:31:28,392
Okay, I will listen to you.

843
00:31:28,792 --> 00:31:30,511
As long as we can get Xiaomi,

844
00:31:30,711 --> 00:31:32,231
I will listen to you completely.

845
00:31:42,951 --> 00:31:43,872
Look.

846
00:31:46,471 --> 00:31:47,631
It's over 560,000.

847
00:31:47,711 --> 00:31:49,112
That's a lot of money.

848
00:31:49,392 --> 00:31:49,992
Well,

849
00:31:50,072 --> 00:31:51,992
I planned to work hard this year

850
00:31:52,072 --> 00:31:52,752
and save up

851
00:31:52,832 --> 00:31:54,472
half a million by the end of the year.

852
00:31:54,552 --> 00:31:55,151
I didn't expect

853
00:31:55,231 --> 00:31:56,712
my kids would get the child support

854
00:31:56,792 --> 00:31:57,832
and accomplish my goal.

855
00:31:57,912 --> 00:31:59,072
Don't spend it recklessly.

856
00:31:59,632 --> 00:32:00,991
When it's spring next year,

857
00:32:01,152 --> 00:32:02,032
the cake shop's rent

858
00:32:02,112 --> 00:32:03,191
will be a big expense.

859
00:32:03,271 --> 00:32:03,832
Also, we need

860
00:32:03,912 --> 00:32:05,431
to pay the rent for this place.

861
00:32:05,511 --> 00:32:06,312
Well,

862
00:32:06,392 --> 00:32:07,232
with so much money,

863
00:32:07,312 --> 00:32:08,671
should I buy a car

864
00:32:08,792 --> 00:32:10,632
or pay the down payment
for my own place?

865
00:32:12,392 --> 00:32:12,911
Can you

866
00:32:12,991 --> 00:32:14,392
help me decide?

867
00:32:15,191 --> 00:32:16,031
What are you doing?

868
00:32:20,552 --> 00:32:22,431
One, two, three, four, five...

869
00:32:22,912 --> 00:32:24,072
300,000?

870
00:32:24,191 --> 00:32:25,191
Wait,

871
00:32:25,552 --> 00:32:26,232
when did you

872
00:32:26,312 --> 00:32:27,431
save so much money?

873
00:32:27,511 --> 00:32:29,312
My retirement pension
has increased again.

874
00:32:29,392 --> 00:32:31,872
Besides, your cake shop
has been doing well these two years.

875
00:32:32,191 --> 00:32:33,272
So I invest less now.

876
00:32:33,352 --> 00:32:35,031
And I still have my savings.

877
00:32:35,632 --> 00:32:36,752
So together we

878
00:32:36,832 --> 00:32:38,511
